					<![CDATA[
						 <p>I never thought I was gonna get all the answers, and I got em. I got a giant sledgehammer right into my face.</p> <p>Well, still&#8230; what's making those brain tumors? Who does it benefit? What for? Other than that, we now know those phone calling brain parasite bastards were the culprit. This is amazingly creepy and horrifying oh my god.</p> 
