					<item>
				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-1966249#post-3809936</guid>
				<title>(no title)</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-1966249/scp-2315#post-3809936</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Wed, 23 May 2018 10:47:26 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>Rioghail</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>1302192</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>That's an extremely strong final addendum that plays very strongly into the ambiguities which the rest of the test logs have been setting up. I especially like that it actually builds, and follows through on, basic questions (what is going on, how is this happening, where did they get the information, what do the contradictions mean?) that most articles wouldn't bother to answer. A very strong piece.</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
					<item>
				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-1966249#post-3782122</guid>
				<title>(no title)</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-1966249/scp-2315#post-3782122</link>
				<description></description>
