					<item>
				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-1966249#post-2676756</guid>
				<title>Author&#039;s Post</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-1966249/scp-2315#post-2676756</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Tue, 25 Oct 2016 01:43:35 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>WrongJohnSilver</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>2000367</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>This is a long time in coming, and something I resurrected from the depths of my sandbox. The original idea of a phone call from a berating mother came from <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/nexescore" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2228610&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1477360183" alt="Nexescore" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2228610)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/nexescore" >Nexescore</a></span>. The original concept didn't work, but I saw potential and asked to revamp it. I did, but I was ultimately unsatisfied. I waited&#8230; and waited&#8230; and a whole year later, I figured out how I want the story to finish.</p> <p>Yes, I'm going way old-school with my interpretation of D-class, but I don't care.</p> <p>Thanks to <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/twistedgears" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1735681&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1477360183" alt="TwistedGears" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1735681)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/twistedgears" >TwistedGears</a></span> who reviewed this a year ago and convinced me it wasn't ready, then (you're right, it wasn't), and to <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/cyantreuse" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2303803&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1477360183" alt="Cyantreuse" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2303803)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/cyantreuse" >Cyantreuse</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/spookybee" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1953164&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1477360183" alt="SpookyBee" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1953164)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/spookybee" >SpookyBee</a></span>, and <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/gibberingeloquence" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1421648&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1477360183" alt="GibberingEloquence" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1421648)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/gibberingeloquence" >GibberingEloquence</a></span> for the modern review.</p> <p>First photo is mine, second from <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/File:Contrast_enhanced_meningioma.jpg" target="_blank">Wikipedia</a> and is public domain.</p> 
				 	]]>
